    {
      "id": "swap-box-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 385,
      "y": 145,
      "width": 270,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 300002,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 300002,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "SwapProposal_Accept\n\nATOMIC -- all in one\ntransaction\n\n1. validate: Bob owns asset,\n   matches spec\n2. exercise offerCid\n   Asset_Transfer -> Bob\n3. exercise assetCid\n   Asset_Transfer -> Alice\n\ncontroller: Alice\n(she exercises Accept)\n\nBoth 2 and 3 succeed\nor BOTH roll back",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "swap-box",
      "originalText": "SwapProposal_Accept\n\nATOMIC -- all in one\ntransaction\n\n1. validate: Bob owns asset,\n   matches spec\n2. exercise offerCid\n   Asset_Transfer -> Bob\n3. exercise assetCid\n   Asset_Transfer -> Alice\n\ncontroller: Alice\n(she exercises Accept)\n\nBoth 2 and 3 succeed\nor BOTH roll back",
      "autoResize": true
    },
